ddf.security.sts.client.configuration

Interface STSClientConfiguration

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractStsRealm, StsRealm, WssStsRealm

    public interface STSClientConfiguration
    Interface for service containing STS client configurations. This can be used by clients to an STS when they want to communicate with it.
